WEBVTT

00:00:58.208 --> 00:01:02.244
neither is there
any banking facility close to her village.

00:01:02.488 --> 00:01:04.314
It would have been so easy

00:01:04.408 --> 00:01:08.658
if Radha could give a command 
on her cellphone in her own language

00:01:08.658 --> 00:01:10.854
and the money could be transferred,

00:01:10.884 --> 00:01:13.448
and she could receive 
a confirmation in her language,

00:01:13.508 --> 00:01:16.124
it would be a happy Diwali for her family.

00:01:16.448 --> 00:01:19.564
To bring happiness into the
lives of people like Radha,

00:01:19.588 --> 00:01:25.928
a technology was needed that was easy to
operate and could empower the people.

00:01:27.048 --> 00:01:30.144
My work began with this thought in mind.